Package dia

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsensusSpectrumReader
    This class read in multiple consecutive SWATH spectra in retention time and analyze them together so consensus information among multiple spectra can be utilized to analyze DIA data
    SWATHMGFGenerator
    Take in a SWATH file and a output file from Harklor http://proteome.gs.washington.edu/software/hardklor/ Generate a IDA-like mgf file that associate all precursor in the SWATH window with each SWATH MS/MS spectrum
    SWATHMSPLITSearch
    Initial try on searching SWATH data with M-SPLIT
    SWATHStatistics
    This class holds a series of utility static method to compute various statistics for SWATH spectra
    SWATHUtils
    Some utility function for SWATH data
